text: A reminder of our open house shindig later this afternoon. Come say hi to our neighbors, even if it’s for a few minutes. Let’s have a strong Uncorked showing!

<!channel> Looking forward to the shindig tonight! Have fun, make sure to eat up, and be responsible tonight! You gotta work tomorrow :stuck_out_tongue:

Safety is our paramount concern! If at anytime you feel you (or someone else) is unsafe to drive or even get themselves home, please let Stephanie and I know - we’ll make sure everyone gets home safe.

Have fun meeting our neighbors!
